Description:
High-explosive rounds utilized by light cannon weapons, such as the Mk6X series. Effective on light or medium-type warships.

Effective at disabling components within ships, at a reduced effectiveness on armor penetration. Works best after a salvo of AP rounds.

Size: 120mm
Role: Offensive
Armor Penetration: 30 cm
Component Damage: 45 hp
Penetration Depth: 15 m
